Il Festival Transeuropa ho lö mincha duos ans ed es ün evenimaint/forum/conferenza politic, culturel ed artistic chi unescha bgers differents formats. Nus, l'organisaziun European Alternative chi sto davousvart, fains que uossa daspö 10 ans. Nus vains dimena già bgera experienza. Que as tratta d'ün evenimaint da chaminer chi ho mincha vouta lö in ün'otra cited. L'ultima vouta, avaunt duos ans, essans stos a Belgrad, dimena üna cited dadour l'Uniun Europeica. Quist an, 2017, vulaivans ir a Madrid per bgers differents motivs.
